            <exercise> <!-- todo: turn into WW -->
            <statement>
                <p>
                    <ol>
                        <li><p>Verify that the value <m>-1</m> is a solution to the absolute value equation <m>\abs{\frac{x-3}{2}}=2</m>.</p></li>
                        <li><p>Verify that the value <m>\frac{2}{3}</m> is a solution to the absolute value equation <m>\abs{6x-5}\lt 4</m>.</p></li>
                    </ol>
                </p>
            </statement>
            <solution>
                <p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>
                            <p>We will substitute the value <m>\substitute{-1}</m> into the absolute value equation <m>\abs{\frac{x-3}{2}}=2</m>:
                                <md>
                                    <mrow>\abs{\frac{x-3}{2}}\amp=2</mrow>
                                    <mrow>\abs{\frac{\substitute{-1}-3}{2}}\amp\stackrel{?}{=}2</mrow>
                                    <mrow>\abs{\frac{-4}{2}}\amp\stackrel{?}{=}2</mrow>
                                    <mrow>\abs{-2}\amp\stackrel{?}{=}2</mrow>
                                    <mrow>2\amp\stackrel{\checkmark}{=}2</mrow>
                                </md>
                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li><p>We will substitute the value <m>\substitute{\frac{2}{3}}</m> in the absolute value inequality <m>\abs{6x-5}\lt 4</m>
                                <md>
                                    <mrow>\abs{6x-5}\amp\lt 4</mrow>
                                    <mrow>\abs{6\cdot\substitute{\frac{2}{3}}-5}\amp\stackrel{?}{\lt} 4</mrow>
                                    <mrow>\abs{4-5}\amp\stackrel{?}{\lt} 4</mrow>
                                    <mrow>\abs{-1}\amp\stackrel{?}{\lt} 4</mrow>
                                    <mrow>1\amp\stackrel{\checkmark}{\lt} 4</mrow>
                                </md>
                            </p>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </p>
            </solution>
        </exercise>

